: <<'=cut'

=head1 helpers for unix C<date> command

=head2 the %DATE_FMT

is a collection of ready to use date formats, available are:

    human

=head2 examples

    date +$DATE_FMT[human]

=cut

my% DATE_FMT

DATE_FMT=(
    human '%A, %d %B %Y'
)

